t support worship and spiritual growth."}]]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"card","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"DOVVSU Ambassador & Warrior Queen"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-muted)]","children":"DOVVSU Ambassador and Worship Warrior Queen, using music and ministry to advocate for dignity, safety, and restoration."}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"card","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl","children":"Awards Spotlight"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--text-muted)]","children":"The success of her single \"This Far\" earned nominations and recognition including Songwriter of the Year, Female Vocal Performance, and Gospel Song of the Year at major 2023 Ghana music awards platforms."}]]}]]}],null,["$","$L2",null,{"children":["$","$3",null,{"name":"Next.MetadataOutlet","children":"$@4"}]}]]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
